{
  "stem": "5225.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he say, hey don't buy by the Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot say nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hey, go away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He has a right to, to boycott your stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "According to the government, he has a right, and do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So always was-- So what we did, like, for example, we got that Gentile girl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We took it already out a license on her name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we put her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after then, was one, a shoemaker-- he was a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We build them up so he be a, a seller for this one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We only charge him what the material cost and the work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Any profit that makes after the work is his.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, Europe was a difference, because the work was cheap, but the food was cheap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For example, if you buy a pair of pants for $2-- the whole pants-- and the material cost you a $1.50, so what cost you--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How you can sell it for $2 if the material cost $1.50?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the lining-- and this will cost you $0.20.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So $0.30 for the work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you got $2.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You sell it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You got $0.30.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You make 10 pairs a day, you got $3 a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And $3 a day was average what a factory man worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because used-- they didn't hire Jews to a factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even they-- a Jew-- a Jew-- a Jew what has the factory, he wouldn't hire a Jew to the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he was scared that they're going to put a fire on the factory or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never hired a Jew to the factory, even if it was a Jewish factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the Jewry must be self-- supporting themself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a average what-- listen, $3 a day, you're not alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Your wife helped out, if you're married.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
